{"TopicId":183725,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Copy and paste problem","CreatedByName":"SiriusRocketry","CreatedById":178125,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-14T01:35:25Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"SiriusRocketry","CreatedById":178125,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-14T01:35:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, I\u0027ve pasted a story I write into the forum reply-box to save re-writing it out. However, the text pastes in bold, and the first words of every line won\u0027t un-bolden. Is there a fix? Is this a known problem?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-14T01:42:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223582663\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022183725\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221555205725\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022178125\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SiriusRocketry\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, SiriusRocketry said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, I\u0027ve pasted a story I write into the forum reply-box to save re-writing it out. However, the text pastes in bold, and the first words of every line won\u0027t un-bolden. Is there a fix? Is this a known problem?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe only\u00A0thing I know of that might work is\u00A0when you first paste the text in, you should see a black line at the bottom with the option to remove formatting.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SiriusRocketry","CreatedById":178125,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-14T01:59:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223582667\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022183725\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221555206171\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160462\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022James Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 minutes ago, James Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe only\u00A0thing I know of that might work is\u00A0when you first paste the text in, you should see a black line at the bottom with the option to remove formatting.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks, it worked! I think you deserve a rep for that. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}